@startuml Sequence_Authentication

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Auth API" as API
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Email Service" as Email

== Registration ==
User -> Client: Fill registration form
Client -> Client: Validate form
Client -> API: POST /api/auth/register
API -> API: Validate data
API -> DB: Check if user exists
DB --> API: User not found
API -> DB: Create user account
DB --> API: User created
API -> Email: Send verification email
Email --> User: Verification email
API --> Client: Success response
Client --> User: Show success message

== Login ==
User -> Client: Fill login form
Client -> API: POST /api/auth/login
API -> DB: Verify credentials
DB --> API: User credentials
API -> API: Generate JWT token
API -> API: Generate refresh token
API --> Client: Return tokens
Client -> Client: Store tokens
Client --> User: Redirect to dashboard

== OAuth Login ==
User -> Client: Click Google login
Client -> Client: Redirect to Google OAuth
Google --> Client: OAuth callback
Client -> API: POST /api/auth/oauth
API -> Google: Verify token
Google --> API: User info
API -> DB: Create/Update user
DB --> API: User data
API -> API: Generate tokens
API --> Client: Return tokens
Client --> User: Redirect to dashboard

@enduml

